BLUEBIRD

EMPLOYEE REFERRAL PROGRAM TEMPLATE

The Bluebird Template is a powerful solution for your employee referral program. With this template, your employees have access to all the tools they need to promote your products and services, monitor referral activity, and receive rewards. The Bluebird Template supports multiple payment options, including PayPal, gift cards, and vouchers, and is available in 20 languages.
This employee referral template is built with cutting-edge web development technologies, including Bootstrap 4 Framework, HTML5, CSS3, and JQuery. It is fully responsive and compatible with all devices and browsers, providing a seamless user experience.
TRY IT FREE
LIVE PREVIEW
This employee referral template offers a hassle-free registration process for employees. Traditional registration and login forms are available, but businesses can also use a one-click access link or customize the form to collect additional information from advocates. With the Bluebird Template, businesses can streamline the referral process and improve data collection to make better hiring decisions.

The Bluebird Template's 15 sharing channels make it easy for your employees to be brand advocates. This employee referral program template provides a range of popular referral channels, including the referral link, email widget, WhatsApp, Twitter, and LinkedIn. With these tools, your employees can easily share your products and services with their network, boosting engagement and driving more referrals to your business.

With the employee stats section, your employees can track their referral performance and focus on the advocacy tools that work best. This feature allows employees to quickly review their total referrals and rewards, view their referral history, track employee referral bonuses, and see the status of their referrals.



EMPLOYEE INSIGHTS

EMPLOYEE PAYMENT METHODS

Make it easy for employees to get rewarded with the Bluebird Template's multiple payment options. With prepaid gift cards, Swags, and PayPal cash available, you can activate different payment methods to allow your employees to choose how they want to get paid. These are attractive options for building an employee referral program that motivates your employees to refer qualified candidates.
